version_description:
We continue to work hard to improve your BMO Digital Banking Experience. In this release:
- Fixed a bug where some users were not able to deposit checks
- We listened to your feedback and made your overdraft line of credit more visible
- You can now see check numbers for electronic checks
- Loan account payments now display payment breakdown details
- Improved the Check Deposit feature to capture check images easier
- Improved the transaction filtering experience
- Made minor enhancements to your login experience
- Squashed a few bugs that popped up recently
